		<title>貓咪摸著摸著就突然咬人？其實是牠的「應激反應」在作祟！</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/02/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e6%91%b8%e8%91%97%e6%91%b8%e8%91%97%e5%b0%b1%e7%aa%81%e7%84%b6%e5%92%ac%e4%ba%ba%ef%bc%9f%e5%85%b6%e5%af%a6%e6%98%af%e7%89%a0%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e6%87%89%e6%bf%80%e5%8f%8d%e6%87%89/</link>
		
